description: Pupils this year receive results based on predicted marks, including Brintha Yasodaran, who attained 12 A* grades.
title: Isle of Man GCSE grades 'not easily gained'
title_page: Isle of Man GCSE grades 'not easily gained' - BBC News
maintext: "It feels strange because to some degree I feel like I haven't completed all the work that I need to do to deserve an A*, I haven't sat an exam or had to go through the stress.
